PRIVACY POLICY
Services is provided by WildSparrowScream at no cost and is intended for use as is.
WildSparrowScream is committed to handling your personal information with utmost care and respect. In order to promote transparency and ensure that our guests can easily comprehend and navigate through our privacy practices and principles, we have designed our privacy policy accordingly.
If you reside in California, the collection and handling of information during gameplay is subject to additional privacy terms outlined in Appendix A.
If you are located in the European Economic Area or the UK, there are also additional privacy terms specified in Appendix B that apply to the handling of your personal information.
Information We Collect
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. The Personal Information that we collect is used for providing and improving the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
We may collect certain information about you when you use our Services. This information may include:
Device Information: We may collect information about the device you use to access our Services, including the hardware model, operating system and version, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information.
Usage Information: We may collect information about how you use our Services, including the games you play, how long you play them, and other gameplay data.
Information You Provide: We may collect information that you provide to us, such as when you register for an account, make a purchase, or contact us for support.
Camera, Photo Gallery, and Microphone Access: Some of our games may request access to your device's camera, photo gallery, or microphone. We only use this information to provide specific features within the game, and we do not share this information with third parties.
How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including to:
Provide and maintain our Services;
Analyze and improve our Services;
Personalize your experience with our Services;
Respond to your requests, questions, and feedback;
Detect, prevent, and address fraud and other illegal activity;
Provide customer support;
Send you promotional messages, such as offers and updates about our Services, subject to your preferences;
Comply with our legal obligations.
We do not share your personal information with third parties except in the following circumstances:
With service providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who help us provide and support our Services.
For legal reasons: We may disclose your information if we believe that such disclosure is necessary to comply with the law, protect our rights or the rights of others, prevent fraud, or respond to a government request.
In connection with a business transaction: If we sell or transfer all or a portion of our business or assets, we may disclose your information to the buyer or transferee.
The app does use third-party services that may collect information used to identify you.
Link to the privacy policy of third-party service providers used by the app
Google Play Services
AdMob
Unity ADS
ironSource
Advertising
We work with third-party advertising networks, including Admob and Unity ADS, to display advertisements in our games. These networks may collect certain device information, such as a unique device identifier, and may use this information to deliver targeted advertisements to you. We do not share your personal information with these advertising networks.
Log Data
We want to let you know that if an error occurs while using our Service, we can collect data and information about your phone called Log Data. This Log Data may include your device's Internet Protocol ("IP") address, device name, operating system version, and the configuration of the app when you use our Service, as well as the time and date of your use of the Service, and other statistics. Please note that this information is collected through third-party products.
Face Data
About face data:
The application does not collect and store data about the face, the application takes a picture only when you press the capture button to create a photo collage.
The application immediately creates an image from a photo taken from the device camera and overlays graphic elements on it. After that it saves it to the device's photo gallery without processing this information outside the device.
The data is not transferred to third parties.
All images created with the application are stored exclusively on the owner's device, to which he has full access.
The device does not collect and use facial data. The app ensures that neither results nor analytical data are stored on devices or servers. Facial data is neither stored, used, disclosed, shared, nor retained by the app. However, it may request permission from the user to save data to the device while using the app.
Cookies
This Service does not use cookies, but some third-party code and libraries used in the app may use cookies to collect information and improve their services. You can choose to accept or refuse these cookies and be notified when a cookie is being sent to your device. Note that if you refuse our cookies, some parts of the Service may not work properly.
Security
We understand the importance of your trust in sharing your Personal Information with us and make every effort to safeguard it using commercially accepted methods. However, it is important to note that no method of transmitting or storing data electronically is completely secure and reliable, and we cannot ensure its absolute security.
Links to Other Sites
This Service may have links to other websites, but we don't operate these external sites. It's recommended that you check the Privacy Policy of these websites. We aren't responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.
Changes to Our Privacy Policy
We may change this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make changes, we will notify you by revising the date at the top of the policy and, in some cases, provide you with additional notice (such as adding a statement to our website or sending you a notification). We encourage you to review the Privacy Policy whenever you access the Services or otherwise interact with us to stay informed about our information practices and the choices available to you.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at wildsparrowscream@gmail.com.
Children's Privacy:
Wild Sparrow Scream games are not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child under the age of 13, we will take steps to promptly delete the information.
Appendix A. Residents of California:
Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (“CCPA”), California residents have the right to know what personal information Wild Sparrow Scream collects about them, and to request that we delete that information.
Our main focus is on gathering, utilizing, and disclosing consumer information in a de-identified or aggregated form, which does not qualify as personal information under CCPA since it cannot be used to reveal your identity, either directly or indirectly. Consequently, we do not possess specific information regarding the location of the individuals who interact with our games or the ads provided by third parties in our games.
Appendix B. Residents of the European Union (EU):
Under the General Data Protection Regulation (“GDPR”), residents of the European Union have certain rights with respect to their personal information, including the right to access and correct inaccuracies, the right to erasure, and the right to object to the processing of their personal information in certain circumstances. Wild Sparrow Scream is committed to complying with the GDPR and to providing EU residents with these rights.
Creepy Neighbor: Lie Detector
Attention, citizens! Following the well-known "Events," the world has entered a new era where humans and replicants can no longer coexist in peace and harmony. In response to this threatening reality, governments worldwide have taken decisive measures, enforcing a strict ban on the production of replicants. However, despite official directives, replicants still among us continue to hide in the shadows, preparing their plans for revenge.
In the darkest corners of society, these cunning beings form underground communities and illegal laboratories. Using our own technology, they create exact human replicas to infiltrate our homes, spreading fear and chaos among peaceful citizens.
Hide and Seek Rust City Escape
The World after an Atomic Nuke War, all surviving cities on the Earth are contaminated with radiation. In the last days Wasteland’s scavengers are trying to attack the last survivors.
+ Run straight to surviving shelters
+ Be wary of Wasteland's scavengers; use any means necessary to remain undetected
+ Look for objects on the ground and hide
Game Features:
+ Atmospheric graphics
+ Addictive gameplay with easy control
+ Many levels to test your wits
+ Sufficient variety of skins for survivors and Wasteland scavengers
+ Fairly challenging levels
Meownite Art: Color by Number
Meownite, a Relaxing Color-by-Numbers Game for All Cat Lovers and Fortnite Fans. Dive into a world of creativity by coloring illustrations of your favorite characters as adorable cats. Follow the numbers to realize the creators' vision or unleash your creativity and create unique, stylish looks!
Features of the Meownite game:
+ Charming illustrations: Your favorite characters as the cutest cats!
+ Ease of use: Intuitive interface.
+ Easily save your work on your device and share it with friends.
+ Fast and exciting process: Enjoy captivating coloring with an intuitive interface.
+ Rich color palette: Find the perfect color combinations for your masterpieces.
+ Many familiar characters from different seasons and battle passes.
Police Chase: Pursuit Patrol
Police Chase: Pursuit Patrol - a game that will give you adrenaline and thrilling sensations of police chases right on your mobile device! Join the police squad on their exciting missions to combat crime in the city. Break-ins, car thefts, fleeing from the law - you'll have to chase and stop the most dangerous criminals, driving a police car in thrilling pursuits.
Game Features:
+ Dynamic pursuits
+ Crazy shootouts
+ Stylish graphics
+ Multiple types of weapons
+ Police siren
+ Bullettime slowmo
+ Police car tuning
+ Various cars to choose from including APC
