Luminti: Magic Golden Hour App
Easily find the golden hour, or sunrise and sunset times with Luminti. Whether you're at your current location or planning a future photo shoot, simply open the app to see when the golden hour starts and ends. Luminti is designed to simplify capture the perfect moment, providing photographers with up-to-date information. Access accurate Golden Hour data worldwide with ease. Make the most of outdoor photography by knowing the best time to shoot using Luminti.
Dino T-Rex: The Volcanic Exodus. Endless Runner Game
In the Jurassic World, the Great Volcanic Eruption has occurred. The Earth is in danger. The fate of a little dinosaur is in your hands!
+ No step back!
+ Overcome obstacles
+ Collect coins and keys
+ Unlock and explore new worlds
+ Collect all avatars
Only you can help the T-Rex and his friends survive. Good luck!
