Police Siren : Sound and Light
Turn your device into a police siren! The app simulates flashing color lights and siren sounds like on a police car. Just pick one of your favorite siren sounds, set the screen brightness to maximum, hit the start button and you're done!
Remember, you can use the siren start timer to start the draw automatically at an unexpected moment.
Application features:
• Modern interface design with smooth animations
• Stylish graphics
• Choose of siren sounds
• Some timer variations
• Multiple siren flashing speeds
• Convenient color change for each part of the siren for variations
